Package: CepalStatR
Title: R Interface to the ECLAC Statistical API
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R: c(person("Henry", "Osorto", email = "henry.osorto@unah.edu.hn",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4334-9179")))
Description: Tools to explore metadata and retrieve indicators from the statistical
portal of the Economic Commission for Latin America and the Caribbean.
Provides a reproducible interface to access the CEPALSTAT API, organize
data into tidy formats, and generate both static and interactive
visualizations in R.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/Henry-Osorto/CepalStatR,
